    <item>
      <title>5 分钟简单生成指定形状的词云</title>
      <link>https://xzywisdili.netlify.app/blog/20230426/2023-04-26-generatewordcloudin5minutes/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Apr 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://xzywisdili.netlify.app/blog/20230426/2023-04-26-generatewordcloudin5minutes/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;群里有人问，想要做一张这样的指定形状的词云：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img
    class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34;
    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
    decoding=&#34;async&#34;
    fetchpriority=&#34;low&#34;
    alt=&#34;photo_2023-04-26_10-26-15.jpg&#34;
    src=&#34;https://s2.loli.net/2023/04/26/6Sl3DX27eC4ZxiM.jpg&#34;
